name: Model_1
command: python3 /inference.py --pb /model1.pb --input_images /lattice/dataset/#datasetname/ --mode image; pushd /lattice/dataset/#datasetname; mkdir training; mkdir training/labels/; mkdir training/images; mkdir ImageSets; cp /inference_output/predictions/* training/labels/; mv *.{jpg,png} training/images/; popd
